  .h2.page-title About Us

  %h4 Our Mission

  %p.text-long
    Our aim is to make <i>Brassica</i> crop data openly accessible and available in a
    standardised and well-described manner. We collaborate with
    = succeed ',' do
      = link_to 'Elixir', 'https://www.elixir-europe.org/about-us'
    = link_to 'Bioschemas.org', 'http://bioschemas.org/'
    and
    = link_to 'Biosamples', 'https://www.ebi.ac.uk/biosamples/'
    to make the hosted data findable and interoperable with analysis tools and
    re-usable among the scientific community.


